'''ᱟᱵᱩ ᱫᱷᱟᱵᱤ''' ({{IPAc-en|US|ˈ|ɑː|b|uː|_|ˈ|d|ɑː|b|i}}, {{IPAc-en|UK|ˈ|æ|b|uː}}; {{lang-ar|أَبُو ظَبِي}} ''{{transl|ar|Abū Ẓabī}}'' {{IPA-ar|ɐˈbuˈðˤɑbi}})<ref name="name">{{cite web |title=How did Dubai, Abu Dhabi and other cities get their names? Experts reveal all |publisher=UAE Interact |date=3 October 2007 |accessdate=5 April 2013 |url=http://www.uaeinteract.com/news/rss-news.asp?ID=24335 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407043402/http://www.uaeinteract.com/news/rss-news.asp?ID=24335 |archivedate=7 April 2014 }}</ref>  ᱫᱚ ᱭᱩᱱᱟᱭᱴᱮᱰ ᱟᱨᱚᱵᱽ ᱮᱢᱤᱨᱮᱴᱥ ᱨᱮᱭᱟᱜ ᱨᱟᱡᱽᱜᱟᱲ ᱟᱨ ᱫᱚᱥᱟᱨ ᱵᱟᱹᱲᱛᱤ ᱦᱚᱲ ᱠᱚ ᱛᱟᱦᱮᱸᱱ ᱠᱟᱱ ᱵᱟᱡᱟᱨ ᱠᱟᱱᱟ ᱾ ᱭᱩ ᱮ ᱤ ᱨᱮᱭᱟᱜ ᱮᱭᱟᱭ ᱜᱚᱴᱟᱝ ᱮᱢᱤᱨᱮᱴᱥ ᱠᱷᱚᱱᱟᱜ ᱱᱚᱣᱟ ᱫᱚ ᱡᱚᱛᱚ ᱠᱷᱚᱱ ᱢᱟᱨᱟᱝ ᱟᱜ ᱠᱟᱱᱟ ᱾  ᱟᱵᱩ ᱫᱷᱟᱵᱤ ᱫᱚ ᱯᱟᱨᱥᱤᱭᱟᱱ ᱩᱯ ᱫᱚᱨᱭᱟ ᱨᱮᱭᱟᱜ ᱛᱞᱟ ᱫᱚᱨᱭᱟ ᱫᱷᱤᱯ ᱨᱮ ᱢᱮᱱᱟᱜ-ᱟ ᱾ ᱒᱐᱑᱙ ᱦᱟᱹᱵᱤᱡ ᱛᱮ ᱟᱵᱩ ᱫᱷᱟᱵᱤ ᱵᱟᱡᱟᱨ  ᱨᱮᱭᱟᱜ ᱦᱚᱲ ᱮᱞ ᱫᱚ ᱑ᱹ᱔᱕ ᱢᱤᱞᱤᱭᱚᱱ ᱾ ,<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://worldpopulationreview.com/world-cities/abu-dhabi-population/ |title=Abu Dhabi Population 2019 (Demographics, Maps, Graphs)|date=May 12, 2019|website=World Population Review}}</ref> ᱟᱵᱩ ᱫᱷᱟᱵᱤ ᱨᱮᱭᱟᱜ ᱥᱟᱢᱚᱴ ᱦᱚᱲ ᱮᱞ ᱫᱚ ᱒᱐᱑᱖ ᱥᱟᱞ ᱥᱩᱫᱷᱟᱹ ᱛᱮ 2.9&nbsp;ᱢᱤᱞᱤᱭᱚᱱ ᱾ <ref>{{cite web|url=https://scad.ae/Release%20Documents/SYB_2018_EN_9Sep%20_Chart%20Correction.pdf|title=Statistical Yearbook of Abu Dhabi 2018|last=|first=|date=|year=2016|website=scad.ae|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170821181258/https://www.scad.ae/en/pages/statistics.aspx?topicid=24|archivedate=21 August 2017|url-status=dead|access-date=}}</ref>



